{
  "stem": "7358.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Uh, Ludwipol was the, the, the county seat, so to speak, the center town, where the government used to have all, all their buildings to administrate the entire area, with all the villages that I mentioned to you before.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Before the Russians left the city prior to the German entry, they burned down the city completely, because they felt that there were too many-- too-- it would-- that would help the Germans a lot, if the city was not left intact.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "As a result, the town was burned down, and, and, and they had to find another place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they had selected a village called Moczulanka.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It's a, it's a Russian name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And in that, in that little village, they, they made a county seat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "As a result, we-- my uncle went into that area.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he managed to obtain-- to rent a room for us, a big room in a, in a farmer's house.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we all moved into this village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we were already free citizens.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The Russians came in, and they established a government.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And, of course, the Germans had retreated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And sort of we returned to be normal human, human beings at that point.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We lived in this village for about six months, approximately.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And at that point, the Russians had made a declaration that everyone that was a Polish citizen prior to the war has an option either to remain in the territory or to be repatriated deeper into Poland, because this area was going to be annexed by Russia as part of the war bounty, and it no longer going to belong to Poland.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "The border was moved further up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So in line of Jewish tradition always to move to the west, we decided that we would be repatriated.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
